# *H	Available targets:
# *H		all:	compile everything
# *H		run:	run G4/7400 simulation
# *H		debug:  run gdb debugger under graphical environment
# *H		trace:  run G4/7400 simulation and output execution statistics
# *H		clean:	remove intermediate files
# *H
# *H	$Log: makefile $
# *H
#================================================================

